#

Bourbon Glazed Salmon with Garlic Mashed Potatoes

30 min
$15
600 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Fish

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh Protein

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main CourseSide Dish

Tags:

EasyQuickComfort Food

Description

A sweet and savory salmon dish paired with creamy garlic mashed potatoes that’s both easy to make and delicious.

Ingredients

  • salmon fillets: 2 (6 oz each)
  • bourbon: 1/4 cup
  • brown sugar: 2 tablespoons
  • soy sauce: 2 tablespoons
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • potatoes: 4 medium
  • butter: 4 tablespoons
  • milk: 1/4 cup
  • garlic powder: 1 teaspoon
